              "free_text": [
                " The neutrons were generated by bremsstrahlung",
                "photons striking a 2-in.-thick Pb target, and then were",
                "moderated into a 1/E spectrum by a 2-in. -thick",
                "polyethylene block next to the source.",
                "Neutron velocities were measured by time-of-flight with",
                "a resolution of 50 nsec/m."
              ]
            }
